<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>Today’s enterprises are quickly adopting cloud-based solutions for business applications and Identity as a Service (IDaaS), such as Okta and Oracle IDCS, for single sign-on (SSO) and more. While remarkably convenient, a cloud-based architecture creates its own architectural and integration challenges that have typically been solved by an on-premise web access management (WAM) solution.</body>
